# Typing frame 1: head dipped 1px (looking at keyboard), right hand
# forward. The empty top row + dropped forehead create a visible "bob"
# at half-block scale — the character pulses gently while typing.
@frame 0
. . . . . . . .
. n H H H H n .
n H H H H H H n
H S e S S e S H
. S S S m S S .
. n S S S S n .
. B B B B B B .
B B B B B B B B
B B B B B B B B
. B B B B B B S
. S . . . . . .
